Guidelines for this table:

  • Only add entries for items that have been created/added to teamcenter
  • In Teamcenter, Item ID and Item Name should be identical
  • Item Description (Part Description) should include details about the name/info of the item
  • If unsure about naming of an item, refer to this page → CAD Naming Convention
